atric cardiologist who just might be a match, and Dylan invites her to come home with him to Los Angeles for Thanksgiving. He may be jealous of the doctor, she may be sending new vibes in Dylan\'s direction, but can either see the signals? And is it inevitable that life imitates art?\r\n-', 'Blu-ray', 1, 1, '', 0, '2020-05-01', '', '2020-04-13 13:01:53', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::MA15+\r\nAustria::12\r\nBrazil::14\r\nCanada::14A\r\nChile::14\r\nDenmark::A\r\nFinland::K-12/9\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nIndia::A\r\nIreland::16\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::PG12\r\nMalaysia::18\r\nMexico::B15\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::A\r\nPeru::14\r\nPhilippines::R-13\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::M18\r\nSouth Korea::18\r\nSpain::12\r\nSweden::Btl\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R', 18),
