ed to Ponce de Leon and a tear of mermaid.\r\n-\r\nClaudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil\r\n\r\nCaptain Jack Sparrow (Johnny Depp), along with the feared pirate Edward Teach, a.k.a. Blackbeard (Ian McShane), and a mysterious woman from his past, Angelica (PenÃ©lope Cruz), race to the infamous Fountain of Youth. Meanwhile, the Spanish have sent some ships to go looking for the Fountain and to counter them, the English have sent their own ship under the Captainship of the pirate-turned-privateer Captain Hector Barbossa (Geoffrey Rush). While Blackbeard is seeking the Fountain to Save his own skin, Barbossa has a vendetta of his own. Who will be the one to reach the Fountain of Youth before the others?\r\n-\r\nsrijanarora-152-448595', 'Blu-ray', 1, 1, '', 0, '2020-05-01', '', '2020-04-14 11:28:41', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, 'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nBrazil::12\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-11/9\r\nGermany::12\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIreland::12A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nMalaysia::P13\r\nMaldives::15+\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNorway::11\r\nPeru::Apt\r\nPhilippines::G\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::12+\r\nSingapore::PG\r\nSouth Africa::13\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::7\r\nSweden::11\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nTurkey::7+\r\nUnited Kingdom::12A\r\nUnited States::PG-13', 12),
