n of a deadly race-car crash helps saves the lives of his peers, Death sets out to collect those who evaded their end.\r\n-\r\nIMDb Editor\r\n\r\nWhile watching a car race at McKinley Speedway, Nick O\'Bannon has a premonition of a car crash that will result in many casualties, including several people that are in the audience. Nick convinces his girlfriend Lori, along with his friends Hunt and Janet to leave. A security guard named George Lanter, along with a racist named Carter, a mother and her two sons, and several other people follow Nick out. Shortly after they leave, Nick\'s premonition comes true. When survivors start dying, Nick, his friends, and George must try to find the remaining survivors and save them from Death before it is too late.\r\n-\r\nRebekah Swain\r\n\r\nIn a car race in McKinley Speedway, Nick has a premonition of a deadly car crash with many casualties in the audience and convinces his girlfriend Lori and his friends Hunt and Janet to leave the place. They are followed by a security guard named George Lanter, a racist man, a mother with her children, and a mechanic. Shortly after they leave, the premonition comes true. When the survivors start dying, Nick, Lori, and George try to save the remaining victims from being killed. Can they save everyone in time?\r\n-\r\nRebekah Swain', 'Blu-ray', 1, 1, '', 0, '2020-05-01', '', '2020-04-20 02:16:17', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::R18+\r\nAustria::14\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nChile::14\r\nFinland::K-18\r\nFrance::12\r\nGermany::18\r\nHong Kong::III\r\nIceland::16\r\nIreland::15A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::R15+\r\nLithuania::N-16\r\nMalaysia::18SG\r\nMexico::C\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::R-13\r\nPortugal::M/16\r\nRomania::I.M.-18\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::M18\r\nSouth Africa::16\r\nSouth Korea::18\r\nSpain::13\r\nSweden::15\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUkraine::16', 16),
