 drawn into a battle for the survival of her world.\r\n-\r\nJwelch5742\r\n\r\nIn the future, Jake, a paraplegic war veteran, is brought to a moon, Pandora, which is inhabited by the Na\'vi, a humanoid race with their own language and culture. Those from Earth find themselves at odds with each other and the local culture.\r\n-\r\nahmetkozan', 'Blu-ray', 1, 1, '', 0, '2020-05-01', '', '2020-04-27 13:27:44', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nAustria::12\r\nBrazil::10\r\nCanada::G\r\nChile::TE\r\nChina::(Banned)\r\nCzech Republic::12\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-13\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nHong Kong::IIA\r\nIceland::10\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIreland::12A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nLithuania::N-7\r\nMalaysia::P13\r\nMexico::B\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNorway::11\r\nPeru::Apt\r\nPhilippines::PG-13\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::12+\r\nSingapore::PG\r\nSouth Africa::13\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::7\r\nSweden::11\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nTaiwan::GP\r\nUnited Kingdom::12\r\nUnited States::PG-13', 12);
