hile Dillinger falls in love for Billie Frechette and Melvin and his men stakes her out trying to catch the outlaw.\r\n-\r\nClaudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil', 'Blu-ray', 1, 1, '', 0, '0000-00-00', '', '2021-01-10 06:33:07', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::MA15+\r\nAustria::14\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-15\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nHong Kong::IIB\r\nIceland::16\r\nIndia::A\r\nIreland::15A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nMalaysia::18SG\r\nMexico::B15\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::R-13\r\nPortugal::M/16\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::NC-16\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::18\r\nSweden::15\r\nSwitzerland::14\r\nTaiwan::R-12\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R', 18),
